  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0dd3.\u0d91\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d89\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db6\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0da7 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dd1\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Pressure on Basil to remove G.L",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chairman of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna, Professor G.L. It is reported that a group of non-members of parliament are putting pressure on the national organizer of the party, Mr. Basil Rajapaksa, to remove Mr. Peiris from that position.",
        "Accordingly, it is stated that it includes a secretary of the party, a chairman of a major government institution related to the environment and a governor.",
        "In addition, it is also said that these three persons are recently 'engaged in a race' to get the vacant position of MP if Mr. Dhammika Perera resigns.",
        "In the meantime, a spokesperson of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna mentioned that Prof. G.L. It can be believed that the removal of Mr. Peiris from the party presidency will happen in the future. However, he said that it is not possible to say whether the removal will be done at the upcoming party convention or on another date.",
        "The General Secretary of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna, Member of Parliament Mr. Sagara Kariyawasam emphasized in a press conference of the party that the future decision regarding the positions of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna will be taken by the party's executive members.",
        "He emphasized this by the chairman of the party, Prof. G.L. During the questioning by the journalists whether Mr. Peiris intends to take disciplinary action as a party for holding a press conference separately with Mr. Dallas Alahapperuma and the group."
      ],
